high_descs: Turn around and walk forward then turn right and walk up to the table just right of the stove
Pick up the furthest salt shaker from the table
Turn right and walk up to the small dark table
Put the salt shaker on the small table
Turn around and walk back to the table just right of the stove
Pick up the salt shaker from the table
Turn right and walk up to the small dark table
Put the salt shaker on the small table just left of the other one
anns.task_desc: Put the salt shakers on the small table

high_descs: Turn around and face the white table to the right of the stove.
Pick the salt shaker up that is behind another shaker on the counter.
Go right and face the black table to the left of the counter.
Put the salt shaker down on the black table.
Turn around and face the white table again.
Pick up the salt shaker from the table.
Go right and face the black table to the left of the counter.
Put the shaker down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers down on a table.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the table beside the stove
Pick up the salt shaker on the table
Turn right then face the black shelf
Put the salt shaker on the shelf to the right
Turn  left then go back to the table
Pick up the salt shaker on the table
Turn right then head to the black shelf
Put the salt shaker on the black shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the two salt shaker on the black shelf
